{"tid":1415493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我哋不割蓆 不分化 不篤灰！！！！！","createTime":"2019-08-05T13:47:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T22:43:33.000Z","uid":76543,"like":99,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"0ee881be061885552d0ef25923357887dcdd7f91","tid":1415493,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:47:52.000Z","msg":"我明白前線好多情緒要發洩 今晚<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>一定唔同你哋割</strong></span></span><br />\n但係之後一星期<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>交番俾和理非做嘢先</strong></span></span><br />\n休息又好 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>對準番政權</strong></span></span> 到<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>和理非回合</strong></span></span> 當鞏固民意 做番啲文宣<br />\n<br />\n引用天琦一句：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">當然，真正的公義還未來臨，你們或許因而心中充滿憤怒，這乃是人之常情。但我懇請你們不要被仇恨支配自己，在危難中，仍要時刻保持警覺與思考。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n今晚大家好好發洩 然後休息<br />\n到和理非諗下一個星期點樣做好唔好<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>光復香港<br />\n時代革命</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"58f680e5e9446cc261328eb45f76dee38afdead6","tid":1415493,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:48:05.000Z","msg":"不割蓆"},{"pid":"0736f48f03808fa3ae1dace29c30bfcf951eb8e6","tid":1415493,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:48:15.000Z","msg":"不分化"},{"pid":"ceef9153e74517c271301cd2e15d0d0054344a6d","tid":1415493,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:48:25.000Z","msg":"不篤灰"},{"pid":"7e01f246f01ae229e616d8942ebf08becf89087f","tid":1415493,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:48:37.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"bbeb4573bcfb3b8f821981feb3ef8493592ae8d7","tid":1415493,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB